"    - `order_note`: Customer notes attached to orders\n"
"\n"
"    Messages are sorted by newest first by default.\n"
"\n"
"    **Deep Linking:**\n"
"    - For `source='contact_form'`: Use `message_id` to navigate to message "
"detail\n"
"    - For `source='order_note'`: Use `order_number` to navigate to order "
"detail\n"
